<%- include('header') %>
    <table style="width:100%;max-width:620px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e3edf8;border-bottom:4px solid #74ba41;">
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 0 30px 20px">
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Dear
                        <%= translate('$.email') %>,</p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Welcome to Decot! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">To complete your registration and start using our secure e-signature platform, please click the button below to verify your email address.</p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;"><b>Verify Email</b></p>
                    <a href="#" style="background-color:#004522;border-radius:4px;color:#ffffff;display:inline-block;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;line-height:44px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0 30px">
                        <%= translate('$.code') %>
                    </a>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>This OTP is valid for
                        <%= translate('$.codeExpiredTime') %> hours.</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;"><strong>Security Tips:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>This verification link is for your account only. Please do not share it with anyone.</li>
                        <li>Keep your Decot password confidential. Don't share it with anyone, including Decot staff.</li>
                        <li>Be cautious of phishing attempts. Decot will never ask you for your password via email.</li>
                        <li>If you suspect any unauthorized activity on your account, please reset your password immediately and contact Decot Support.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 25px; "><strong>Don't recognize this activity?</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; ">If you didn't create a Decot account, please disregard this email.</p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 25px; "><b>Regards,</b></p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; ">The Decot Team</p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; "><strong>P.S.</strong> This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 25px; "><strong>Important Notice:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Beware of phishing scams. Always ensure you're visiting the official Decot website (
                            <a href=" <%= translate( '$.websiteLink') %>">
                                <%= translate('$.websiteLink') %>
                            </a>) when entering sensitive information.
                        </li>
                    </ul>


                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <%- include('footer') %>